入，直至另行通告為止。<br />\n<br />\n理大呼籲學校師生、職員及公眾人士在此期間，不要進入理大校園。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%90%86%E5%B7%A5%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E5%B7%B2%E8%A7%A3%E5%B0%81-%E5%B0%8D%E9%96%8B%E6%9A%A2%E9%81%8B%E9%81%93%E4%BE%86%E5%9B%9E%E7%B7%9A%E4%BA%A6%E5%B7%B2%E9%87%8D%E9%96%8B-042146082.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E5%25B0%2581-%25E5%25B0%258D%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%259A%25A2%25E9%2581%258B%25E9%2581%2593%25E4%25BE%2586%25E5%259B%259E%25E7%25B7%259A%25E4%25BA%25A6%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E9%2587%258D%25E9%2596%258B-042146082.html&d=GkFIyr4nU57GJWscoxyRLSPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=d2bf7a36\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%90%86%E5%B7%A5%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E5%B7%B2%E8%A7%A3%E5%B0%81-%E5%B0%8D%E9%96%8B%E6%9A%A2%E9%81%8B%E9%81%93%E4%BE%86%E5%9B%9E%E7%B7%9A%E4%BA%A6%E5%B7%B2%E9%87%8D%E9%96%8B-042146082.html</a>"},{"pid":"0e12bd21070947d3f836bf160c43974ae9130deb","tid":1761673,"uid":307329,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T05:17:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e34183c05480a29783e7c4c01a2dcdd7becdcc7f","tid":1761673,"uid":131122,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e12bd21070947d3f836bf160c43974ae9130deb","tid":1761673,"uid":307329,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"136ef507bba76b6175f75be7ff96e3a1bfea464c","tid":1761673,"uid":131122,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"9c4c6b860c346e186723d4ff6e3d254d95498491","tid":1761673,"uid":307329,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T05:14:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T05:15:20.000Z","msg":"睇新聞話無人阻"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T05:17:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T05:19:59.000Z","msg":"理大校園解封，校方發聲明指校園仍存在不安全因素，而且清理、盤點及修復需時，故校園仍需關閉，只限校方授權人士進入，直至另行通告。不過，仍然有市民在警方解封後即進入校園了解情況。<br />\n<br />\n在理大附近上班的吳小姐走入校園，看到破落的環境後感觸落淚，她形容超級震撼，「喺天橋睇到遮陣嗰陣已經好心悒，入到正門更加崩潰，唔係因為啲建築物有幾爛，而是見到呢兩個星期直播的畫面喺眼前，可想而知當日喺戰場上的學生有幾驚。」她說，希望學生都可以平安回家，見到家人。"},{"pid":"e0bcd8996ad805ea0b6f6995f887f80c59835217","tid":1761673,"uid":131122,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0e12bd21070947d3f836bf160c43974ae9130deb","tid":1761673,"uid":307329,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"136ef507bba76b6175f75be7ff96e3a1bfea464c","tid":1761673,"uid":131122,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"9c4c6b860c346e186723d4ff6e3d254d95498491","tid":1761673,"uid":307329,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T05:14:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T05:15:20.000Z","msg":"睇新聞話無人阻"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T05:17:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T05:20:09.000Z","msg":"你又望望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cf25032baf8b51ba5bb9a20fbb50d0984a932d0","tid":1761673,"uid":131122,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T05:23:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c85601f68f2f66957f0ee3ffe7376ba6b8242ed1","tid":1761673,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T05:26:19.000Z","msg":"回收物資ok<br />\n掃地洗tg由番比popo"},{"pid":"f2c737ab0bf5e86252c152c5f622dd76c145e03c","tid":1761673,"uid":325827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"989e928660a3a40a7995643725b68371eb5a1dfe","tid":1761673,"uid":131122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T05:13:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />需要<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔需要"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T11:20:07.000Z","msg":"今晚七時有冇人啊？越多人去清潔，早啲可以令學校回復乾淨"},{"pid":"79e0077dd06654464e205c10afafe7e0091e7659","tid":1761673,"uid":111966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2c737ab0bf5e86252c152c5f622dd76c145e03c","tid":1761673,"uid":325827,"like":0,"disli